import { library } from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core';

import {
    faChevronDown,
    faChevronUp,
    faUserCircle,
    faCog,
    faSignOutAlt,
    faFolder,
    faFolderOpen,
    faChevronCircleRight,
    faChevronCircleLeft,
    faBars,
    faPencilAlt,
    faCircle,
    faDotCircle,
    faChevronRight,
    faShieldAlt,
} from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons';

library.add(
    faChevronDown,
    faChevronUp,
    faUserCircle,
    faCog,
    faSignOutAlt,
    faFolder,
    faFolderOpen,
    faChevronCircleRight,
    faChevronCircleLeft,
    faBars,
    faPencilAlt,
    faCircle,
    faDotCircle,
    faChevronRight,
    faShieldAlt
);

import { fabTelegramPlane, faTelegramPlane } from '@fortawesome/free-brands-svg-icons';

library.add(fab, faTelegramPlane);
